"title": "4612: birds",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4612",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Part of the created world, used for food. In OT times they were also used in sacrifices. In Scripture, birds are used in many metaphors.</p>\n<h2>Part of creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:21\">GEN 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:20-Gen1:30\">GEN 1:20–1:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:20\">GEN 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:39\">1CO 15:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:7\">JAS 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>Cared for by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:24\">LUK 12:24</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:26\">MAT 6:26</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:41\">JOB 38:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:11\">PSA 50:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:9\">PSA 147:9</a></p>\n<h3>To be cared for by humanity</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:6-Deut22:7\">DEU 22:6–22:7</a></p>\n<h2>Specific varieties of bird</h2>\n<h3>Raven</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:7\">GEN 8:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:4\">1KI 17:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:11\">SNG 5:11</a></p>\n<h3>Eagle</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:4\">EXO 19:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:27\">JOB 39:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:5\">PRO 23:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:31\">ISA 40:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:16\">JER 49:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:3\">EZK 17:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:33\">DAN 4:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:1\">HOS 8:1</a></p>\n<h3>Hen</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a></p>\n<h3>Cock</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:31\">PRO 30:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:74\">MAT 26:74</a></p>\n<h3>Ostrich</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:13-Job39:18\">JOB 39:13–39:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:3\">LAM 4:3</a></p>\n<h3>Owl</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:6\">PSA 102:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:11\">ISA 34:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:15\">ISA 34:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:39\">JER 50:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:8\">MIC 1:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:14\">ZEP 2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Quail</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:13\">EXO 16:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:31-Num11:32\">NUM 11:31–11:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:40\">PSA 105:40</a></p>\n<h3>Sparrow</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:3\">PSA 84:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:2\">PRO 26:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:29-Matt10:31\">MAT 10:29–10:31</a></p>\n<h3>Stork</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:17\">PSA 104:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:7\">JER 8:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech5:9\">ZEC 5:9</a></p>\n<h3>Vulture</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:23\">JOB 15:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:17\">PRO 30:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:16\">MIC 1:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:8\">HAB 1:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:28\">MAT 24:28</a></p>\n<h3>Birds of prey</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:26\">DEU 28:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:46\">1SA 17:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:4\">1KI 16:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa18:6\">ISA 18:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:9\">JER 12:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:17-Rev19:18\">REV 19:17–19:18</a></p>\n<h2>Protected at the flood</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:20\">GEN 6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:17-Gen8:19\">GEN 8:17–8:19</a></p>\n<h2>Used in sacrifice</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:20\">GEN 8:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:10\">GEN 15:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:14\">LEV 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev12:8\">LEV 12:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:3-Lev14:7\">LEV 14:3–14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:49-Lev14:53\">LEV 14:49–14:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:22-Luke2:24\">LUK 2:22–2:24</a></p>\n<h2>Used as food</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:11\">DEU 14:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev17:13-Lev17:14\">LEV 17:13–17:14</a></p>\n<h2>Some not to be eaten</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:25\">LEV 20:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:13-Lev11:19\">LEV 11:13–11:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:12-Deut14:18\">DEU 14:12–14:18</a></p>\n<h2>Not to be used as an object of worship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:15-Deut4:17\">DEU 4:15–4:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:23\">ROM 1:23</a></p>\n<h2>Appearing in dreams and visions</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:17\">GEN 40:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:6\">ACT 11:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:7\">REV 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:14\">REV 12:14</a></p>\n<h2>Used metaphorically</h2>\n<h3>Of freedom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:6\">PSA 55:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:1\">PSA 11:1</a></p>\n<h3>Of isolation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:7\">PSA 102:7</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Of powerlessness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:11\">HOS 11:11</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Of being trapped</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps124:7\">PSA 124:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:5\">PRO 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:23\">PRO 7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:26\">JER 5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:52\">LAM 3:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:20\">EZK 13:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:12\">HOS 7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:5\">AMO 3:5</a></p>\n<h3>Of cruel invaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:11\">ISA 46:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:49-Deut28:50\">DEU 28:49–28:50</a></p>\n<h3>Of an object of hatred</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:9\">JER 12:9</a></strong></p>",
